sentences: Ludvig Sophus Adolph Theodor Holm  (24 December 1858 - 8 April 1928) was a Danish violinist and composer.

He was for many years Vice-President of the Copenhagen Chamber Music Society and for many years the artistic director of the People's Concerts.
